com.opengamma.strata.pricer.provider

Class NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.pricer.provider.NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NormalVolatilitySwaptionProvider, Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public class NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider
extends Object
implements NormalVolatilitySwaptionProvider, ImmutableBean, Serializable
    Volatility environment for swaptions in the normal or Bachelier model. The volatility is represented by a surface on the expiration and swap tenor dimensions.
